headline: Waters Highlights Continued Progress Towards Sustainability Commitments
summary: Today Waters Corporation (NYSE: WAT) highlighted the company's progress on reducing its environmental impact, becoming more representative of the society we live in, and continuing to enhance our long-term stakeholder value with good governance and effective oversight in its 2024 report.
